# Copy to .dev.vars for `wrangler dev` (git-ignored).
#
# The container app runs OPEN by default (no auth needed) and boots zero-infra
# (in-memory store, deferred DB), so NO secrets are required to deploy.
#
# Optional — set on the CONTAINER (add to envVars in src/index.js, or as wrangler
# secrets wired through) only if you want them:
#   API_KEY=          # require X-API-Key on the data API (else open)
#   DATABASE_URL=     # postgresql+asyncpg://...  durable history (else deferred)
#   REDIS_URL=        # redis://...               shared cache (else in-process)
